links.title: Stocks Fall On These Tech Titans With Market Rally On The Brink
links.description: Dow Jones fell modestly Friday morning, along with the S&P 500 and Nasdaq composite, with struggling stock market rally on the bring. Apple stock fell on earnings while coronavirus cases hit record highs in the U.S. just before Election Day. Amazon.com ( AMZN) and Facebook ( FB) sank on results while Google parent Alphabet ( GOOGL) jumped.
